Package game.risk.controller

Class GameController

java.lang.Object
game.risk.controller.GameController
public class GameController
extends java.lang.Object
Executes the Game's status, allows the command of Forfeiting, conquering a country with the number of armies you want to go with, roll dixe, end a turn and get the winner of the game.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Tejash, Jatin, Lynn, Adityo
